PRIORITIES (LOW->HIGH)
--------------------------
Follow Black Path
	takeAction: true
	action: follow black path
	suppress: stop

Follow Set Colour
	takeAction: colour set
	action: follow colour path
	suppress:

Target Found
	takeAction: change in ultrasonic sensor
	action: set target found to true, move forwards slowly until ultrasonic sensor value increases
	suppress: stop

Shortest Distance
	takeAction: ultrasonic sensor value increases & target found
	action: stop, turn 90 degrees to face target, turn ultrasonic sesnor -90 degrees
	suppress:

Save
	takeAction: target shortest distance
	action: turn on floodlight until target removed
	suppress: stop

Celebrate
	takeAction: targets saved > set value
	action: display message/make noise/move
	suppress: stop

Mission Report
	takeAction: stopped
	action: display stats(targets saved, time taken, distance travelled)
	suppress: 

Set Colour
	takeAction: colour not set
	action: set colour
	suppress: 

Systems Check
	takeAction: button is pressed (RIGHT)
	action: checks if motors have stalled (e.g. Motor.A.isStalled())
	suppress: 

Abandon
	takeAction: button is pressed (LEFT)
	action: move on
	suppress: 

Emergency Stop
	takeAction: button is pressed (ESCAPE)
	action: halt program until restart or exit
	suppress: 
